{"tid":1124831,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好鍾意幫人買M記","createTime":"2019-04-25T09:14:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T09:29:38.000Z","uid":52270,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"88e7650172fd35cc14be7903165e3191fe9d5498","tid":1124831,"uid":52270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T09:14:58.000Z","msg":"我成日都會自願做跑腿<br />\n幫公司啲同事買M記<br />\n然後買完嗰陣一路行一路食鳩晒佢哋啲薯條<br />\n<br />\n有次我食到佢哋大薯條變中薯條<br />\n中薯條變細薯條<br />\n<br />\n佢哋反而冇懷疑 仲屌柒間M記剷得咁少薯條<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係冇得揀 公司附近得一間M記<br />\n所以依然佢哋都會幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa26022cf3ff39ffc7a8637a47184009c96ed6e7","tid":1124831,"uid":249395,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T09:20:31.000Z","msg":"想要個9號餐 送黎我屋企 多謝"},{"pid":"ce6c8595a84468855b84236c31ea32a460a97141","tid":1124831,"uid":107219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T09:20:47.000Z","msg":"好彩我轉栗米杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429db62b260f506900cede749da06db12cd62315","tid":1124831,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T09:24:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.mcdonalds.com.hk/content/dam/hongkong/Chinese/24_hours_mcdelivery/order-by-phone-im-lovin-23382338.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mcdonalds.com.hk%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fhongkong%2FChinese%2F24_hours_mcdelivery%2Forder-by-phone-im-lovin-23382338.png&h=22f2c9bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c925014c71a8b396264bc99e050242b330b9e34b","tid":1124831,"uid":238301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T09:28:53.000Z","msg":"我想要雙層芝士孖堡餐再加個豬柳蛋漢堡"},{"pid":